Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:42.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:45.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the time we got to\NNaraku's Castle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Wolf-Demons\nhad been slaughtered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:53.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:10.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:12.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's trap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:14.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga went after Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:17.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}believing that his comrades\nhad been killed by him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:21.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The glow in his right arm was{\i0} not\n{\i1}from a Sacred Jewel fragment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:24.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With greater ferocity,\NKoga attacked Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:31.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He says this should keep you busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As usual, the ape likes to make\nthings complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While those hotheads\nfight it out their way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we get to take on a demon puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He takes us lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:07.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:10.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're inside Naraku's castle.\NWho knows what traps have been laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn these traps.\NI've had just about enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we teach them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:28.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A measly demon puppet...\nis no match against us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Where's he getting\nthat brute strength?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:55.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ooh! The roof's been blown off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The power of that right arm\nisn't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?\NWe have to stop them quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:04.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not Inuyasha who killed\NKoga's friends... It was Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn mutt!\NI'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jumping around, trying to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:54.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Kagome is ever hurt,\nit'd be your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku wants us to fight...\nuntil one of us dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:01.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't intend\nto fall into Naraku's trap, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've pushed me this far...\NI'm not holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!\NI'm avenging my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:12.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:33.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Did I claw you just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:39.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad...\NHe smashed my arm bone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is... the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:49.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mr. Wolf Man...\nnow you have no regrets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:57.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I'll let you have your last dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening?! Aren't they dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They may be dead,\nbut they want to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're so happy\nthey can dance with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:16.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:20.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one\nwho killed my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:48.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move...\NWhat's happened to my body?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The poison in the fragment in your arm\nis starting to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's time to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't move, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fragment you have\nimbedded in your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a fake Sacred Jewel made\nfrom crystallized poison and miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You jumped around so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it sped up\nthe spread of the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:37.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, I'll have the {\i1}real{\i0}\nfragments you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's the sacred arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not impressive at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I won't let you get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare\nlay a finger on Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:31.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:35.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mr. Wolf Man,\nyou didn't complete your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:43.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! As if I'd die\nfrom a blow from that puny wolf cub!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:47.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to fight me...\nin that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lemme tell you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll show you no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:56.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bathing me in the blood\nof the Wolf-Demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and setting that fool on to me\nwasn't nice at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but what I can't stand more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:05.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is the scent of Naraku\nthat reeks from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:07.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just the thought of Naraku enables me\nto move my wounded body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:31.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She thwarted the Tetsusaiga\nwith such little wind power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With just one arm,\NI can draw only half its power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the Wind Sorceress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:42.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The wind in this castle\nis under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance of the Wind Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This...is her ghostly wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The point where the winds collide...\nthe Wind Scar!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where Tetsusaiga can attain\nits greatest power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I cut it through...\NI can destroy her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's happening?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see the Wind Scar\nanywhere around Kagura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the Wind Sorceress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:51.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wind in this castle\nis under my control!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:55.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That means...\nmy wind is also under her control!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's like he can't move his right arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This time... Hit the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is she aiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's sacred arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura's ghostly wind\nis being blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is a way\nto create the Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop dallying!\NHurry and shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, if this arrow hits you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even you could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:38.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But... I must have faith in Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This arrow...\nis purifying my ghostly wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:16.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The ghostly wind has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:22.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! Wind is easily created!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the two ghostly winds\nappear once more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Wind Scar...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be created!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:48.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Wind Scar...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:14.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That scar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The castle is disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This castle was an illusion, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I let her get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't use my broken right arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I couldn't deliver the finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The color in the skin is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The poison\nfrom the fake fragment is spreading!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?!\NWe can't let him die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no use. The barrier is too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It deflected your hands, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we must do something quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I tried to kill Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:46.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!\NYou were just tricked by Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even Inuyasha has no desire\nto settle it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since we both fell\nright into Naraku's trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,if you only want to save his life,\nthere's a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold out your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll chop it off with the fake jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Just wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There must be another way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't touch the barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:18.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but Kagome, the sacred arrow\ncan dissolve the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura who killed my comrades\nand Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}with my own hands...\NSomeday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will kill them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Koga will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:37.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He looks like a very proud man.\NBetter to let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a funny way to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:41.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but we're used to being tricked\nby Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:45.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then... let's see how strong\nthe other proud one is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's... fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:02.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He fought so hard.\NEven Inuyasha must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We should let him sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She had the same spider-shaped\nburn scar on her back... like Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:14.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A woman who has the same scent\nas Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fifty years ago,\nin order to steal the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku tricked Inuyasha\nand Kikyo to battle each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Die, Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:54.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is gathering\nthe Sacred Jewel fragments...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and his evil power is growing steadily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku has been cursed by Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a Wind Tunnel in his right hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:12.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, the Wind Tunnel\nwill devour Miroku himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:15.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must destroy Naraku\nbefore that happens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango's father\nand fellow demon slayers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}were killed before her very eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku had resorted to the dirty trick...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:26.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- {\i1}of using her brother Kohaku.{\i0}\N- Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:32.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was also Naraku who gave the\ndeadly poison wasps to Sesshomaru...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:36.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and deceived Sango\ninto fighting Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He never dirties his hands...\na despicable coward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:03.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someday, we'll get him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:33.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura... so you came out of this alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:34.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You tricked me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:41.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You never told me about the power\nof that Inuyasha's sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sword that cuts through\nthe Wind Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:48.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wondered just how powerful it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but if you can make it back alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess it wasn't much of a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you did trick me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:27.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-that's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't forget, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:40.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your heart is in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:48.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's simple to turn you back\ninto what you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:52.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Kagura... do not forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:59.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In essence...\nyou were created from a part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:52.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We met up with a girl named Koharu\nwho is an acquaintance of Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! You asked her to bear your\nchild when she was just eleven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:58.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is definitely a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:24:01.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must leave this village quickly,\nfor Koharu's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:03.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:05.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The villagers are attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.74,0:24:08.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet that female demon\nis behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:13.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Kagura's Dance and Kanna's Mirror!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.41,0:24:14.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
